description: Macy's is set to open the exclusive doors to New York Fashion Week for fans everywhere as Macy's Presents Fashion's Front Row makes the high-fashion runway accessible to all. Featuring the fall season’s hottest looks, Fashion’s Front Row will highlight collections by the nation’s best design talent and performances from superstars Ariana Grande and Flo Rida, at an extraordinary evening that brings the runway closer to fans. The high-fashion runway will feature fall collections including the world-exclusive debut of Betsey Johnson’s designs inspired by DreamWorks Animation’s TROLLS, Calvin Klein, I.N.C. International Concepts, Rachel Rachel Roy, Tallia, Tommy Hilfiger, William Rast, and more. Macy's Presents Fashion's Front Row will benefit the Council of Fashion Designers of America Foundation, Inc. and Ronald McDonald House New York with 100% of the purchase price of all tickets sold, minus Ticketmaster and facility fees.
